<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Worst Rap Lyrics Throughout the Years</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Easily sort throughout the decades and discover the worst rap lyrics of each year.">
  <meta property="og:title" content="Discover the Worst Rap Lyrics Throughout the Years" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Each year is unique in it's own way with it's own terrible lyrics" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://badrapapi.com/year" />

  <link rel="canonical" href="https://badrapapi.com/year" />

  <!-- CSS only -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous" />
  <!-- JavaScript Bundle with Popper -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('./navbar'); %>
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="mt-3">Worst Rap Lyrics by Year</h1>
    <% var worstYear = 0; var numInYear = 0 %>

    <% for(var i=0; i<data.length; ++i) { %>
    <% if(data[i].songs_in_year.length > numInYear) { %>
    <% numInYear = data[i].songs_in_year.length%>
    <% worstYear = data[i].year %>
    <% } %>
    <% } %>
    <p>Easily sort through all the years of horrible rap lyrics. Each year showcases all the rappers who are currently featured having a bad lyric in that speicific year. Some rappers appear multiple times within a single year.</p>
    <p>Currently, <b><code><%= worstYear %></code></b> is the year with the worst lyrics.</p>


    <div class="row">
      <% for(var i=0; i<data.length; ++i) { %>
      <% var addedArtists = new Array() %>
      <hr>

      <div style='margin-bottom: 25px;' class="col-md">
        <a href='/year/<%=  data[i].year %>'>
          <h2><%= data[i].year %></h2>
        </a>
      

        <% for(var y=0; y<data[i].songs_in_year.length; ++y) { %>

        <% if(addedArtists.indexOf(data[i].songs_in_year[y].artist) == -1) { %>
        <% addedArtists.push(data[i].songs_in_year[y].artist) %>
        <div>
          <span><%= data[i].songs_in_year[y].artist %></span>
        </div>
        <% } %>


        <%  } %>
        <% if(data[i].songs_in_year.length == 1) { %>
          <p style='margin-top: 10px'><b><%= data[i].songs_in_year.length %> lyric from <%= addedArtists.length %> artist</b></p>
          <% } else { %>
          <p style='margin-top: 10px'><b><%= data[i].songs_in_year.length %> lyrics total across <%= addedArtists.length %> different artists</b></p>
          <% } %>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md">

        <% if(data[i].songs_in_year.length == 1) { %>
        <div>
          <% if(data[i].songs_in_year[0].explicit) { %>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" className="bi bi-explicit" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path d="M6.826 10.88H10.5V12h-5V4.002h5v1.12H6.826V7.4h3.457v1.073H6.826v2.408Z" />
            <path d="M2.5 0A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0 2.5v11A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 2.5 16h11a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 2.5-2.5v-11A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 13.5 0h-11ZM1 2.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 2.5 1h11A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 15 2.5v11a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-11A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 1 13.5v-11Z" />
          </svg>
          <% } %>
          <p style='display: inline;'><i>"<%= data[i].songs_in_year[0].lyrics %>"</i> - <%= data[i].songs_in_year[0].artist %></p>
        </div>
        <% } else { %>
        <% const r = Math.floor(Math.random() * data[i].songs_in_year.length)%>
        <div>
          <% if(data[i].songs_in_year[r].explicit) { %>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" className="bi bi-explicit" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path d="M6.826 10.88H10.5V12h-5V4.002h5v1.12H6.826V7.4h3.457v1.073H6.826v2.408Z" />
            <path d="M2.5 0A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0 2.5v11A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 2.5 16h11a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 2.5-2.5v-11A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 13.5 0h-11ZM1 2.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 2.5 1h11A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 15 2.5v11a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-11A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 1 13.5v-11Z" />
          </svg>
          <% } %>
          <p style='display: inline;'><i>"<%= data[i].songs_in_year[r].lyrics %>"</i> - <%= data[i].songs_in_year[r].artist %></p>
        </div>
        <% } %>

      </div>


      <% } %>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center" style='font-size: 10px; margin-bottom: 50px; margin-top: 50px;'>Icons made by <a href="https://www.flaticon.com/authors/sumberrejeki" title="SumberRejeki">SumberRejeki</a> from <a href="https://www.flaticon.com/" title="Flaticon">www.flaticon.com</a></div>

  </div>
</body>

</html>